[SN]TITLE[SN]
How to bring a penguin puppet to life

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
From War Horse to the Lorax -  some of the biggest stars of the theatre aren't humans, but the puppets they operate.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
28 November 2016 Last updated at 06:48 GMT
In Mr Popper's Penguins, not one, but ten penguin puppets steal the show.
Actor Lucy Grattan shows us how she brings the penguins to life.
